бувала боротися, аналізувала, питала себе «чому».\nА потім махнула рукою й така: ну, shit happens. Буває.\n\nТому офіційно повідомляю: я йду в цей чудовий стан під назвою «ганьба та самоаналіз».\nБуду там рефлексувати і, можливо, навіть знайду вихід.\n\nА поки — я на паузі. До 1 серпня.\nЗі мною...","board":{"node_id":"Qm9hcmQ6MzE0NzU5NTMwMTQ2Njg3MzYy","image_cover_url":"https://i.pinimg.com/200x150/15/49/68/154968ba9c65392c7bf3be2e5f840f8e.jpg","followed_by_me":false,"cover_images":{"222x":{"url":"https://i.pinimg.com/222x/15/49/68/154968ba9c65392c7bf3be2e5f840f8e.jpg","width":222}},"collaborated_by_me":false,"id":"314759530146687362","image_thumbnail_url":"https://i.pinimg.com/upload/314759530146687362_board_thumbnail_2026-04-23-21-37-05_10694_60.jpg","type":"board","image_cover_hd_url":"https://i.pinimg.com/474x/15/49/68/154968ba9c65392c7bf3be2e5f840f8e.jpg","section_count":0,"images":{"170x":[{"url":"https://i.pinimg.com/170x/4e/dd/e2/4edde2658a6cb6d88ddf3fff5c0a5987.jpg","width":170,"height":212,"dominant_color":"#72704C"},{"url":"https://i.pinimg.com/170x/ec/eb/0e/eceb0ed9e41f4ca378a6cb7e83d7ee37.jpg","width":170,"height":212,"dominant_color":"#121808"},{"url":"https://i.pinimg.com/170x/9a/08/c7/9a08c7daf644431a43eb2a06a268c778.jpg","width":170,"height":212,"dominant_color":"#3C5512"},{"url":"https://i.pinimg.com/170x/c6/66/73/c66673c565988b99152652365dc0456a.jpg","width":170,"height":212,"dominant_color":"#C5B373"},{"url":"https://i.pinimg.com/170x/e5/6d/51/e56d5184c87db409d8b5eccb8d9682a3.jpg","width":170,"height":212,"dominant_color":"#CFCCD2"},{"url":"https://i.pinimg.com/170x/5b/83/d5/5b83d5f70893b3df8d1999538aa8f528.jpg","width":170,"height":212,"dominant_color":"#6B4D35"},{"url":"https://i.pinimg.com/170x/d9/50/13/d950138cf3030b155ceae9600a6c583d.jpg","width":170,"height":212,"dominant_color":"#A0877F"},{"url":"https://i.pinimg.com/170x/6a/f6/54/6af654c2f27c07b03a7ea8f7d3e7abfa.jpg","width":170,"height":212,"dominant_color":"#110F10"},{"url":"https://i.