eese menjadi kombinasi yang unik saat mengunyah bersamaan dengan cireng nya  • 1bungkus isi 6pcs ayam suwir,bakso,seblak,sosis pedas,sosis bolognase dan keju  cara membuat :  • Tuang bumbu bubuk kewadah/mangkuk • Tambah kan air panas kurang lebih 200ml aduk hingga larut lalu masukkan cireng nya  enjoy testing","board":{"node_id":"Qm9hcmQ6ODUwMTI0OTM1ODUxMDY3NDEx","image_cover_url":"https://i.pinimg.com/200x150/b6/ae/b0/b6aeb0f4bbc4666abd1da3feb34a8db3.jpg","followed_by_me":false,"cover_images":{"222x":{"url":"https://i.pinimg.com/222x/b6/ae/b0/b6aeb0f4bbc4666abd1da3feb34a8db3.jpg","width":222}},"collaborated_by_me":false,"id":"850124935851067411","image_thumbnail_url":"https://i.pinimg.com/upload/850124935851067411_board_thumbnail_2026-04-25-09-43-23_57779_60.jpg","type":"board","image_cover_hd_url":"https://i.pinimg.com/474x/b6/ae/b0/b6aeb0f4bbc4666abd1da3feb34a8db3.jpg","section_count":0,"images":{"170x":[{"url":"https://i.pinimg.com/170x/ae/78/01/ae7801109c4286d75e5cc0a711393604.jpg","width":170,"height":170,"dominant_color":"#D9A06F"},{"url":"https://i.pinimg.com/170x/9a/7d/62/9a7d62e0c29d4ea137097aebbaee2445.jpg","width":170,"height":114,"dominant_color":"#949599"},{"url":"https://i.pinimg.com/170x/07/87/cc/0787ccdf3b263f2fbefe28b38ddf51b5.jpg","width":170,"height":229,"dominant_color":"#FFFFFF"},{"url":"https://i.pinimg.com/170x/85/0f/95/850f956a96ca9acdbe12fa6a00503b6f.jpg","width":170,"height":131,"dominant_color":"#FFFFFF"},{"url":"https://i.pinimg.com/170x/44/9a/0a/449a0a9a3c8560ed1d6bad3bb72916e0.jpg","width":170,"height":127,"dominant_color":"#F7F7F7"},{"url":"https://i.pinimg.com/170x/3a/81/99/3a819993dbaf654f52931d8614e999c8.jpg","width":170,"height":127,"dominant_color":"#FDFDFD"},{"url":"https://i.pinimg.com/170x/f9/4a/0f/f94a0f9cc9121b10971a2b94feeea8a9.jpg","width":170,"height":170,"dominant_color":"#E7EFF2"},{"url":"https://i.pinimg.com/170x/11/fe/98/11fe988d493066ab6e17d07d169d137d.jpg","width":170,"height":127,"dominant_color":"#FFFFFF"},{"url":